#: tycontrols.design.rsdtformname
msgid "TyControls Form"
msgstr "TyControls 窗体"

#: tycontrols.design.rsdtformdescription
msgid "A borderless form descending from TTyForm, with a top-aligned TTyTitleBar already attached (drag to move, double-click to maximize). Point its Controller at your main window's style controller to theme it, or lay out your controls below the bar."
msgstr "一个继承自 TTyForm 的无边框窗体，已附带一个顶端对齐的 TTyTitleBar（拖动可移动，双击可最大化）。将其 Controller 指向主窗口的样式控制器即可应用主题，或在标题栏下方布置你的控件。"

#: tycontrols.design.rsdtmainformname
msgid "TyControls Main Form"
msgstr "TyControls 主窗体"

#: tycontrols.design.rsdtmainformdescription
msgid "A themed TTyForm carrying its own TTyStyleController, with the form and the title bar already associated to it — the root window for a TyControls application."
msgstr "一个带有自身 TTyStyleController 的主题化 TTyForm，窗体与标题栏均已关联到它——TyControls 应用程序的根窗口。"

#: tycontrols.design.rsdtappname
msgid "TyControls Application"
msgstr "TyControls 应用程序"

#: tycontrols.design.rsdtappdescription
msgid "A graphical TyControls application. The main form is a themed TTyForm (custom title bar + style controller); the tycontrols package is added automatically."
msgstr "一个图形化的 TyControls 应用程序。主窗体是主题化的 TTyForm（自定义标题栏 + 样式控制器）；tycontrols 包将被自动添加。"

#: tycontrols.design.rsdtabouttitle
msgid "About TyControls"
msgstr "关于 TyControls"

#: tycontrols.design.rsdtabouttagline
msgid "Themed LCL control library"
msgstr "主题化 LCL 控件库"

